We serve a diverse client base in terms of size and industry. We have approximately 36,600 clients, or nearly 19,100 clients based on parent company grouping, none of which constituted more than one-half of one percent of our revenues for the year ended December 31, 2022. We stored data for over 6.5 million persons employed by our clients during the year ended December 31, 2022. 

